{"tid":790931,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"友邦業績等侯區","createTime":"2018-08-23T11:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T03:25:35.000Z","uid":150989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6671f43107918d8eb2e51da5f6e7ee063b186e","tid":790931,"uid":150989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:29:39.000Z","msg":"友邦保險(<a href=\"http://01299.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01299.HK&d=9KtZC7Xczbv2fjYgGjHB7S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=8646faa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01299.HK</a>)  -0.700 (-1.020%)    沽空 $3.24億; 比率 23.726%   將於下周五(24日)公布截至6月底止七個月業績，本網綜合8間券商，料友邦保險今年上半年新業務價值介乎19.23億至19.9億美元，按實質匯率(Actual exchange rates,AER)計算﹐較2017年同期16.05億美元，按年增加19.8%至24%，中位數為19.54億美元，按年增加21.7%。<br />\n<br />\n綜合6間券商，料友邦保險2018年上半年稅後營運溢利(OPAT)介乎24.54億至26.82億美元，較2017年上半年22.33億美元，按年增加9.9%至20.1%，中位數為26.13億美元，按年升17%。<br />\n<br />\n此外，本網綜合7間券商，料友邦保險今年上半年的年化新保費介乎31.06億至32.01億美元，按年增加6.9%至10.2%。中位數為31.52億美元，按年增加8.5%。<br />\n<br />\n高盛預期，按實際匯率計算，友邦保險2018年上半年新業務價值按年升23%至19.69億美元，同期稅後營運溢利按年升20.1%至26.82億美元，年化新保費按年升10.2%至32.01億美元。該行預期本港業務第二季強勁復甦，尤其在訪港內地旅客部分，將部分地抵銷中國業務因首季業績突出而放緩的影響。該行將在友邦保險公布業績時，對中國業務策略、東盟市場增長及派息與資本政策的看法。<br />\n<br />\n摩根士丹利估計，友邦今年上半年新業務價值按實質匯率計可按年升21%(按固定匯率則升17%)至19.39億美元，料香港業務上半年新業務價值(按實質匯率計)可按年升6%至7.7億美元，內地業新業務價值可按年升45%至5.47億美元，估計泰國業務新業務價值可按年升15%至2.06億美元。<br />\n<br />\n券商│今年上半年新業務價值預測│按年變幅(按實質匯率(AER))<br />\n德銀│19.9億美元│+24%<br />\n瑞銀│19.9億美元│+24%<br />\n星展唯高達│19.84億美元│+23.6%<br />\n高盛│19.69億美元│+22.7%<br />\n摩根士丹利│19.39億美元│+20.8%<br />\n匯豐環球研究│19.33億美元│+20.4%<br />\n麥格理│19.32億美元│+20.4%<br />\n摩根大通│19.23億美元│+19.8%<br />\n按友邦2017年上半年新業務價值16.05億美元計算。<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n綜合6間券商，料友邦保險2018年上半年稅後營運溢利(OPAT)介乎24.54億至26.82億美元，較2017年上半年22.33億美元，按年增加9.9%至20.1%，中位數為26.13億美元，按年升17%。<br />\n券商│今年上半年稅後營運溢利預測│按年變幅<br />\n高盛│26.82億美元│+20.1%<br />\n麥格理│26.51億美元│+18.7%<br />\n德銀│26.13億美元│+17%<br />\n瑞銀│26.12億美元│+17%<br />\n摩根大通│24.74億美元│+10.8%<br />\n匯豐環球研究│24.54億美元│+9.9%<br />\n按友邦2017年上半年稅後經營溢利22.33億美元計算。<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n此外，本網綜合7間券商，料友邦保險今年上半年的年化新保費介乎31.06億至32.01億美元，按年增加6.9%至10.2%。中位數為31.52億美元，按年增加8.5%。<br />\n券商│今年上半年年化新保費預測│按年變幅<br />\n高盛│32.01億美元│+10.2%<br />\n匯豐環球研究│31.71億美元│+9.1%<br />\n摩根大通│31.63億美元│+8.8%<br />\n麥格理│31.52億美元│+8.5%<br />\n德銀│31.38億美元│+8.0%<br />\n摩根士丹利│31.28億美元│+7.6%<br />\n瑞銀│31.06億美元│+6.9%<br />\n按友邦2017年上半年年化新保費29.06億美元計算。<br />\n(fc/w)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2018-08-23 16:25。)"},{"pid":"28856d237e1a923f220a7a5022d287a8b70ff993","tid":790931,"uid":150989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"美銀美林料內險股中期新業務價值增長弱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667da0e6f4cbdb44a836eac08c8fff9432461577","tid":790931,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28856d237e1a923f220a7a5022d287a8b70ff993","tid":790931,"uid":150989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"美銀美林料內險股中期新業務價值增長弱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:32:30.000Z","msg":"即係大升<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77d074966a7f1cb5ece459d897a31228c362fab","tid":790931,"uid":150989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:34:38.000Z","msg":"業績遠差過預期<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605babf28f65d17348132adfc8c09f97a4d1cd7a","tid":790931,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:42:48.000Z","msg":"eps跌左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b0207b30b765731882e6f1ddbc1c8363bc7bd3","tid":790931,"uid":197441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:44:05.000Z","msg":"幾點公布？"},{"pid":"065360cfb43928302a568d70a481ba9244496e50","tid":790931,"uid":150989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b0207b30b765731882e6f1ddbc1c8363bc7bd3","tid":790931,"uid":197441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:44:05.000Z","msg":"幾點公布？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:45:01.000Z","msg":"已經出左"},{"pid":"d2cf087ff1ebbc2f39e7380aafde1f3f27444279","tid":790931,"uid":150989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:47:15.000Z","msg":"友邦保險截至6月底止6個月盈利16.62億美元，較去年同期減少近一半。公司將財政年度結算日由11月30日，更改為12月31日。中期息每股29.2港仙。<br />\n<br />\n集團上半年總收益155.62億美元，下跌逾18%，當中投資回報13.82億美元，下跌逾80%。<br />\n<br />\n按固定匯率計算，上半年新業務價值增長17%，達到19.54億美元，年化新保費增加9%，升至32.52億美元，新業務價值利潤率上升4.4個百分點，達到59"},{"pid":"8e21b622bd9a7e1b36b6dd69436db02edbc9798a","tid":790931,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:48:44.000Z","msg":"今日洗白白"},{"pid":"1e36fb591f21ed25508cd3a689adc44af86fa0cc","tid":790931,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:49:09.000Z","msg":"快d跌返去60<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44952df74bc60ff6b6fb72030c8188d26e12588c","tid":790931,"uid":77626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:02:15.000Z","msg":"差過預期？"},{"pid":"94322148da34ba7d838e72fca3bde1db3e14ddb3","tid":790931,"uid":29295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:05:49.000Z","msg":"新業務價值符預期<br />\n照計唔算差"},{"pid":"a09376d53cbb6b69a1612ee9e5b069f4c6718808","tid":790931,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94322148da34ba7d838e72fca3bde1db3e14ddb3","tid":790931,"uid":29295,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:05:49.000Z","msg":"新業務價值符預期<br />\n照計唔算差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:07:01.000Z","msg":"vitality?"},{"pid":"25a3156843c6362796b4589e559bb97158eb05c0","tid":790931,"uid":178572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:26:51.000Z","msg":"友邦保險 (<a href=\"http://01299.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01299.HK&d=9KtZC7Xczbv2fjYgGjHB7S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=8646faa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01299.HK</a>) 公布，截至今年6月底止六個月業績顯示，按國際財務報告準則，稅後營運溢利按年上升14%至26.53億美元，符合本網早前綜合6間券商料友邦保險2018年上半年稅後營運溢利介乎24.54億至26.82億美元(中位數為26.13億美元)。 公司指，每股股息增加14%至29.2港仙(2017年同期25.62港仙)，反映公司強勁的財務業績及對集團前景的信心，這與公司審慎、可持續及漸進的派息政策相符一致。 期內，友邦保險內涵價值營運溢利按年增19%至41.52億美元；內涵價值營運回報上升70個基點至17%。內涵價值權益為536億美元；內涵價值為520億美元，較2017年或上升12億美元。產生的基本自由盈餘為24.97億美元，按可比基準計算上升11%。自由盈餘為137億美元。集團主要營運公司AIA Co.按香港保險業條例基準計算的償付能力充足率為458%。(ta/w)~ 阿思達克財經新聞 網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=9KtZC7Xczbv2fjYgGjHB7S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=39c87d99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018-08-24 07:32:26"},{"pid":"8523eebeaba9b84235889536263643be6b4f2c64","tid":790931,"uid":69110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:54:36.000Z","msg":"係咁跌"},{"pid":"6a42053123d410d8416e0470939f6e648454f9a3","tid":790931,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:56:46.000Z","msg":"有排跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6e9be416433fbdf3bd5a8898c511d8bb3b7323","tid":790931,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"GG"},{"pid":"d16eead4265bf795b6f9b4dad77a6c3e162a4419","tid":790931,"uid":69913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"友邦出親業績都跌架啦"},{"pid":"e1877eba0d77fe4ec7d9b1ca7366aaa9b27954d6","tid":790931,"uid":180404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d16eead4265bf795b6f9b4dad77a6c3e162a4419","tid":790931,"uid":69913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"友邦出親業績都跌架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:13:34.000Z","ms